~How to Compile~
1. Run Makefile through terminal.
2. Execute the executable with name DSK.

~Expected Inputs~
1. Press keys using mouse left key.
2. Use right button of mouse for zooming a key.
3. Use +/- of keyboard for zooming the whole keyboard at once.

~Notable Defects~
1. The output on output bar may overflow from its boundaries if too many(>80) letters are entered in on line, or more than 4 lines of text is entered.


